These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, musical
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up  | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | western   |
| Sport         | volleyball | golf |
| Transport     | scooter | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: corn, pumpkin
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, adventure
2 different pets are kept: lizard, frog
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike
1. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | corn     | pumpkin |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | animation  |
| Pet           | frog         | lizard     |
| Transport     | scooter   | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
