The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the architect##3
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the architect##1
3. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | sprite     | milk |
| Job         | architect | coach    |
| Pet         | hedgehog         | fish        |
| Transport   | roller         | snowmobile    |

