There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, pepper
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, collecting
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, electronic
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | mirinda |
| Food          | pepper   | grapefruit  |
| Hobby         | fishing | collecting     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | electronic         |

